statlin
-------

Statically linked programs.

* All works (source code, documentation etc.) must be in the Public Domain. 
* Programs should be written in portable ISO C (C90) with POSIX extensions.
* Programs should build and run correctly under any POSIX-compliant OS.
* Programs should be statically linked with no external dependencies.
* Formal verification of new programs is recommended.
* Exceptions to the above criteria must be documented.
